I just said?

42:09.570 --> 42:10.571
Yeah.

42:13.095 --> 42:14.401
And?

42:14.401 --> 42:15.924
I was just thinking
you come in here,

42:15.924 --> 42:17.273
hungover on your day off,

42:17.273 --> 42:18.753
