on this thing

42:18.753 --> 42:20.407
than the whole squad has
in two years.

42:21.321 --> 42:24.237
Yeah, well,
they fucked with my family.

42:26.065 --> 42:27.327
What'd you get on Clay?

42:27.327 --> 42:28.720
- Your beekeeper?
- Yeah.

42:28.720 --> 42:29.895
He's a ghost.

42:30.983 --> 42:32.288
What?

42:32.288 --> 42:34.029
Yeah, all I have
is a birth certificate

42:34.029 --> 42:35.030
and a social.

42:35.727 --> 42:37.163
- The guy's never even
- [SIGHS]

42:37.163 --> 42:38.251
had a bank account,

42:38.251 --> 42:40.558
credit card, flown on a plane.

42:41.080 --> 42:42.734
I ran his prints through
every database

42:42.734 --> 42:44.344
I can think of, no hits.

42:45.650 --> 42:46.912
That's bullshit.

42:46.912 --> 42:48.261
This dude is former military
all day.

42:48.827 --> 42:50.437
No hits. I'm telling you.

42:50.437 --> 42:51.612
Either he's never
been printed,

42:51.612 --> 42:54.310
